openblocks.yacodeblocks
Interface IWorkspaceController

All Known Implementing Classes:
WorkspaceController, YailGenerator
public interface IWorkspaceController

The IWorkspaceController interface defines the public methods that a workspace controller must implement. See WorkspaceControllerHolder for a class designed to hold an instance of a class that implements IWorkspaceController.

Author:
lizlooney@google.com (Liz Looney)
